short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension to help you prepare for DSA

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension is designed to enhance your interview preparation by keeping you on track with solving LeetCode problems daily. It automatically redirects you to unsolved problems and locks your browser at the start of each day, ensuring you stay focused until you solve the assigned problem. The extension monitors your progress, updates redirection based on the problems you've solved, and helps you meet your daily goals, making your practice consistent and effective.
